  "text": "The results obtained in this study by using the EPV-11 modeling software were validated against the results published in the literature. The combined regenerative Brayton/ORC cycle utilizing CO2 in the topping cycle and Iso-pentane in the bottoming ORC was modeled by Dunham et al. [CITATION_1] using the Engineering Equation Solver (EES). Table 10 presents the cycle parameters used in the calculations. The heat input to the topping cycle is assumed to be 100 MW. ",
